---
title: Louisiana BBQ Jackfruit Quesadillas with Pickled Onion Salsa & Plant-Based Sour Cream
description: Stuff flour tortillas with smokey Southern-style jackfruit, bake them with a healthy sprinkle of plant-based cheese, and meet
your new favourite weeknight recipe!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/louisiana-bbq-jackfruit-quesadillas-3e2ee66b.jpg
